title: Episode 105 - East Germany 1950 - 1960
itunes:author: The History of the Cold War Podcast
itunes:summary:
In this episode we examine East Germany politically, economically and socially during the 1950s and in relation to West Germany. Additionally, we examine the first half of the Berlin crisis.

For pictures for this episode and more go to our website at:  www.historyofthecoldwarpodcast.com/
